Web application vulnerability scanner that can be used to automate webserver enumeration and scan web applications for vulnerabilities

WMAP is available as an MSF plugin and can be loaded directly into MSF.

To load in wmap
service postgresql start
msfconsole
load wmap
wmap_
wmap_modules  wmap_nodes    wmap_run      wmap_sites    wmap_targets  wmap_vulns
wmap have these modules 
we use wmap_sites in this event we can add and delete sites
wmap_sites -a <target_ip> now the site is created 
now we use wmap_targets  -t http://<target>
wmap_run -t it will run all available modules from msf console
wmap_run -e runs all the enabled modules and file and dir brutefoce
